description:
We are a highly-specialized software agency, focused on JavaScript development of customized web, mobile and desktop applications.
Our cutting-edge stack of technologies and methodologies includes:
• React Native for hybrid mobile applications;
• ReactJS, Redux, GraphQL, NodeJS, ExpressJS, SailsJS, Meteor for web applications;
• Electron for desktop applications;
• Jest, Mocha, Chai, Sinon, Karma, Jasmine, Enzyme for testing applications;
• Heroku, Amazon Web Services for deployment of applications;
• Photoshop, Sketch, InVision, Zeplin, Moqups, Balsamiq for wireframing, prototyping and designing applications.
We offer full-cycle product development - from UI/UX design, through development, testing and deployment, to support and implementation of new features.
Contact us now on contact@softzen.co and let us discuss your idea!
